{{nosources|date=July 2010}} '''Californium''' is a [[chemical element]]. It is a [[radioactive]] [[metal]]. It has the chemical symbol '''Cf'''. It has the [[atomic number]] 98. Californium is a [[transuranic element]]. It is in nature on Earth but is also in other parts of the universe. Californium does not have many uses. It was [[discovery|discovered]] by [[bombardment|bombarding]] a [[curium]] [[wikt:target|target]] with [[alpha particle]]s ([[helium]] [[ion]]s).
