'''Nobelium''' ({{pronEng|noʊˈbɛliəm}} or {{IPA|/noʊˈbiːliəm/}}) is a [[synthetic element]] with the symbol '''No''' and [[atomic number]] 102.
== Other websites == {{Commons|Nobelium}} {{wiktionary|nobelium}}
